Class PSFieldValue

java.lang.Object
  com.percussion.cms.objectstore.PSFieldValue
All Implemented Interfaces:
IPSFieldValue, Cloneable
Direct Known Subclasses:
PSBinaryValue, PSDateValue, PSTextValue, PSXmlValue
public abstract class PSFieldValue
extends Object
implements IPSFieldValue

Base class for all IPSFieldValue. Implements some of the methods that don't vary across all or many of the components that will be implemented in the CMS layer. Derived classes should override the abstract methods.
